reviewText: Doesn't work with american dvd players. Would have been nice if told this wouldn't work, if i had known this i wouldn't have bought it. Lesson learned.

If you have a Region 2 or Region free DVD player, you should buy this movie today and watch it basically as soon as it arrives at your house.

Movie review: How many thumbs are allowed to be up? These kids in Oregon find evidence that Sasquatch is roaming around. That's all you need to know. Justin Long is hilarious, Joey Kern is hilarious, that kid that played Peter Pan one time is hilarious, Uncle Rico is a sheriff, Carl Weathers is a Bigfoot expert... just trust me on this and watch this movie.
